{
  "primary_issue": "SQL injection vulnerability in the 'selectUser' operation",
  "evidence": "The method `userDao.seletcUser(xingming)` is called with the user-supplied parameter `xingming` without any sanitization or parameterized query. This allows an attacker to inject arbitrary SQL commands.",
  "fix_summary": "Use parameterized queries (PreparedStatement) in the DAO layer for all database operations, especially for the `seletcUser` method. Validate and sanitize all user inputs before using them in SQL queries."
}
